---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- HERO with upfront CTA via Beehiiv + promo -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1 class="brand">Modern Compass</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Helping you find direction in the moments that matter most.
      </p>
      <p class="sublead">
        Modern Compass is a framework for accelerating growth in Self, Trust, Character, and Relationships.
      </p>

      <!-- Promo + Beehiiv embed as a single unit -->
      <div class="newsletter-embed">
        <img
          src="/Newsletter%20Promo.png"
          alt="Join 100+ subscribers and get this digital asset free"
          class="promo-img"
        />
        <script async src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/embed.js"></script>
        <iframe
          src="https://subscribe-forms.beehiiv.com/261a3276-40ab-431a-8523-c85bec095b96"
          class="beehiiv-embed"
          data-test-id="beehiiv-embed"
          frameborder="0"
          scrolling="no"
          style="width: 595px; height: 225px; margin: 0; border-radius: 0; background-color: transparent; box-shadow: 0 0 #0000; max-width: 100%;"
          title="Subscribe to the Modern Compass newsletter"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS MODERN COMPASS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">What Is Modern Compass?</h2>
      <p>
        There are a lot of great self-improvement books, yet many skew academic or abstract. Modern Compass is different.
        It is built around four clear directions that are simple to remember and deep enough to guide real progress.
        It becomes your compass for tracking growth. Each direction has four layers that build on each other.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/Modern%20Compass%20Layers.png"
        alt="Modern Compass layers graphic"
        class="layers-img"
      />

      <p class="sublead centered">
        Each direction builds in layers. Start with the foundation, then move down as each layer builds on the previous one.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Self</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Awareness</li>
            <li>Worth</li>
            <li>Confidence</li>
            <li>Control</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Trust</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Tenets of Trust</li>
            <li>Trust in Humanity</li>
            <li>Informed Trust</li>
            <li>Profound Trust</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Character</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Environmental</li>
            <li>Developed</li>
            <li>Authentic</li>
            <li>Transcending</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="h3">Relationships</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Empathy</li>
            <li>Resonance</li>
            <li>Affinity</li>
            <li>Loyalty</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY IT MATTERS -->
  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Why it matters</h2>
      <p>
        Life does not come with a map, and every choice pulls you somewhere. Without clarity you drift.
        With Modern Compass, you have a tool to orient yourself, test your decisions, and move with confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF AND MOMENTUM -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">Proof and momentum</h2>
      <p>
        Over one hundred subscribers gain monthly insights and use Modern tools like the TimeOS Audit, the Impulse Wallet,
        and the Intention vs Action Activity to reclaim time, take action, and grow with intention.
        There are also 1,000+ followers on TikTok for behind the scenes, insights, and nightly navigation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING NOTE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2 class="h">A personal note</h2>
      <p>
        I created Modern Compass for a couple of reasons. In my late teens and twenties I felt lost with little to give me direction.
        I am writing this for others who feel that way. While this book is not about parenthood, I am also writing what I would want
        my daughters to have as they become adults and learn to navigate life.
        As I close most of my newsletters and TikTok posts, alwaysâ€¦ follow your compass.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Layout helpers */
  .wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .wrap.narrow { max-width: 800px; }
  .section { padding: 56px 0; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .section.alt { background: #f8fafc; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero { padding: 56px 0 12px; text-align: center; background: #ffffff; color: #111; }
  .brand {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    background: var(--gradient); /* uses your site gradient */
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .lead { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 6px 0; color: #222; }
  .sublead { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 18px 0; color: #444; }
  .sublead.centered { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }

  /* Promo + Beehiiv as a single unit */
  .newsletter-embed {
    display: grid;
    justify-items: center;
    row-gap: 8px;
    margin: 12px auto;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .promo-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 420px;
    height: auto;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .beehiiv-embed { display: block; margin-top: -12px !important; }

  /* Content blocks */
  .h { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #111; }
  .h3 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 4px 0; color: #111; }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: #333; }

  .layers-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 12px auto;
    height: auto;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px;
  }
  .card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .card li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .beehiiv-embed { margin-top: -8px !important; }
  }
</style>
